data.description: BACK ON MARKET, BUYERS HOME DIDN’t SELL. Perfectly situated on 2 and a quarter acres; this gorgeous tudor home is surrounded peaceful serentity, nature and privacy while conveniently located in the sought after community of Rockwall, Tx and Rockwall schools. Plant your very own garden, bring your horses or other animals. There is also a small shed with electric and two stalls for keeping horses and other activities. The home greets you with BRAND NEW WOOD LIKE FLOORS, FRESH PAINT and NEW AC UNIT.  Also, offering an impressive amount of space with just about 3800 squ. ft , 4 bedrooms  The Primary bedroom suite downstairs has also beauitful wood like floors, is impressive with a large luxury shower, double vanities and large closet. The living area boasts extra high ceilings that open up into the pristine white kitchen, dining and morning room. An incredible opportunity. Come and get this home while it lasts...
